[texte],text inside brackets\
antiquewhite,color\
,width\
,height\
btm-left ,option : rectangle triangle= number=

slib_out= url for a balloon with text
slib_comment=need wims_version 4.09a,\
<br />for the options :\
<br/>triangle=btm-left or triangle=btm-right or triangle=left-top or triangle=right-top\
<br /> number=some_number (give the name of the css #bubble_number ; \
should be precise if there is several balloon on the same page.
